      "title": "Strong winds expected tonight (7)",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); Department of Meteorology announced that several spells of showers will occur in Sabaragamuwa province and Nuwara-Eliya and Kandy districts.",
        "A few showers may occur in the Western province and Galle and Matara districts.",
        "Strong winds of about (40-50) kmph can be expected at times in the western slopes of the Central hills and the Southern province.",
        "Court rejects police request on protests planned for 8th & 9th July"
